data.value:
Follow these instructions to create your own application for use with idPowerApp.
1. Browse to Azure Portal > Azure Active Directory > App registrations > New registrations - Type in a name e.g. My idPowerApp and select Register 2. Select Authentication > Add a platform > Mobile and desktop applications - Set Custom redirect URIs to http://localhost and select Configure 3. Select Overview and copy the following values into the form below - Application (client) ID - Directory (tenant) ID
